  <brief_title>A Dose Finding Study to Assess the Effect of LIK066 Compared to Placebo or Empagliflozin in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus and Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel-group Dose-finding Study to Assess the Effect of 3 Doses of LIK066 Compared to Placebo or Empagliflozin in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Patients With Heart Failure</official_title>
