  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a dose-finding study to evaluate the efficacy, safety and tolerability of 3 different
      doses of LIK066 compared to placebo or empagliflozin in T2DM patients with heart failure
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
